# ROS2 C++ Hello World Node

This project demonstrates a minimal ROS2 node written in C++ using the `rclcpp` client library.

## ðŸš€ Features
- Custom ROS2 node
- Inherits from `rclcpp::Node`
- Uses `RCLCPP_INFO` logging
- Built with `ament_cmake`
- Compiled using `colcon`

## ðŸ›  Requirements
- Ubuntu 24.04
- ROS2 Jazzy

